article: Hello! I'm Jane. I'm thirteen . I have a sister, but  I don't have a brother. I like games. I often   play soccer with her. I have 2 volleyballs. I like ping-pong, too. I play ping-pong with my friends after school. Do you like games ? Do you play sports every day ?
